We placed our idea here and (as you may find) we've got a lot of negative feedback. People were right. The idea was out of place. But before remove my post from here, I asked Anton (CEO of i-stom.ru. Software for Dentals) if he wants to unite. So together we can build a Blockchain for Dentals and supply chain. Anton agreed and that's how I transformed the initial idea to a bigger one. Honestly, I doubt that we can succeed with our mess ICO here. But I believe, that Blockchain is a future for any tech company and we definitely have to pivot ours.    So if it looks like a scam for you - You are entitled to make such estimates. For startups - its a usual mess situation

Body: You just see an ICO as a means to an end, but it makes very little sense to me, and I don't really care what a definition written by... who knows says:  - If you want to crowdfund a project/product, you shall go to kickstarter or similar platforms.  - If you want to drive the crypto economy or just make profit from it, you can accept bitcoins for your product in your web or create a store in crypto-friendly platforms like OpenBazaar.  Because if we keep seeing this pseudo-"ICOs" as legit, sooner rather than later we will see an ICO for each singular product, a cryptocurrency/token for each singular product, and this is not good for the crypto ecosystem. It is like if you went to the supermarket and you had to buy apples with "applecoins", cucumbers with "cucumbercoins" and condoms with "condomcoins". Or even worst, because each brand would have it's own cryptocurrency, so you should pay in "durexcoins", "trojancoins", "beyondsevencoins", "trustexcoins" or whatever.  This is as inefficient as adding a flux capacitor to your kit (unless you can travel back in time and warn yourself when you were just a boy to not eat so many candies). There is an expression in Spanish to define that: technologic "postureo", or more politely in French: façade.  Want to make a real favour to the crypto world? just announce this kit on the teleshopping claiming that you only accept bitcoins as means of payment.  P.D: just my opinion, nothing wrong with your product and I applaud your innovative vision but, man, you really can do it better; crypto isn't adding anything to your product, just money to your pocket.

Body: You are right: 1- we see an ICO as a tool; 2- we do not use blockchain technology to do something.  We are the next stage of development Blockchain Ecosystem itself: 1st were Bitcoins. Than Wallets, Exchanges, different financial technologies (FinTech).  But how can you buy a bread in your supermarket with your COOLwallet? Or milk? Gas? Maybe house? Or Medicine? So real businesses should accept this COOLcoin from your COOLwallet. How can we (businesses) do this? Ok, I personally can take you COOLcoin and then... I have to pay my workers, suppliers etc. So I need to exchange your coin into real world (fiat) money. And what if all coffee-shops will exchange coins into fiat - it will kill the Economy. So somebody have to put MORE fiat money back into COOLcoins. This is where we (startups from the real world) helps. Basically we take $1 worth of Bitcoin, put it into our business to work. Than we generate $2 worth of it, and putting back to second market to buyback our tokens. With this we: 1- bringing more money (and real value) into Bitcoin Ecosystem itself; 2- making profits for our investors. So they can invest more in other businesses here and make more profits. Now more businesses can accept Bitcoins, replacing fiat money and old economy bit-by-bit. You can by a milk, shoes, medicine, etc.  So, we do not use blockchain technology to do something. We adding value into Bitcoin Ecosystem itself.

My name is Sergey Safronov (username *DentalFx*).  I'm the founder of DENTALFIX - A blockchain company for Dental clinics and the supply chain. We are a group of 2 startup-companies from Dental industry, merging with one primary goal - to create a leader in blockchain health industry. Of course, we are not the only ones fighting for such huge piece of the pie. But we probably the only ones, who truly understands the Dental market, because we are already working on it and making revenue by selling our software and services. With blockchain technology, we see the opportunity to grow beyond our limits, that's why we agreed to take such risks and use this opportunity to launch our initial ICO.   By following the links below you can find a few of my "live" pitches (Disclaimer: some of the information in these videos is outdated) :  https://youtu.be/bqtdJ2o9yOc https://youtu.be/dw2_dWvAE2o                     DentalFix Bounty Campaign  DentalFix -A blockchain company for Dental clinics and the supply chain  WHITEPAPER  ENGLISH https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B2-rqxQ4OfPEV3FkYjNON3lYX3M INDONESIAN https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B2-rqxQ4OfPETzg4RmU5Yl80QTg ITALIAN https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B2-rqxQ4OfPEV3J2RTlkanB4bWc  Official Announcement Thread: LINK  Pre-ICO date: July, 10   DentalFix Bounty Campaign  2% of the DentalFix tokens will be issued for the Bounty Program (equivalent of 30K-100K USD, depends on pre-ICO result).  Participants will be paid at the end of Campaign by stakes basis. Each participant bounty count will be calculated as: Total bounty * Allocated percentage for this part of Campaign / Total participants stakes *Participant stake  Bounty allocation:  1: Signature & Avatar Campaign - 30%  Signature campaign period is divided for 2 parts: 1. preICO Signature campaign  (within 5 days after pre-ICO ends, aprx. 20-30 July 2017) 2. ICO Signature campaign (August 2017) Stakes will be added weekly by Saturdays.  Signature:  Allowed Ranks: Jr member and higher: Jr Member and Member: 0.5 Stake/Week Full and Sr Member: 1 Stakes/Week Hero and Legendary Member: 1.5 Stakes/Week  Avatar: Full member and higher: 0.5 Stake/Week   Rules  1)Minimum 12 constructive posts per week is required 2)Only one account per person. 3)No third parties ads in your signature/avatar. 4)No SPAM (All spam-posts will be deducted from the total; if we’ll find a lot of spam by your account, you’ll be disqualified) 5)No negative trust! (If you’ll receive negative trust (or if you’ll be banned) during campaign, you will be disqualified) 6)Every participant should update signature after pre-ICO (we will change some text) 7)Participants should keep the signature/avatar until the end of ICO Campaign. Management Bounty - 20%  We’ll pay only for high quality translations!  Main thread translation: 50 stakes for translation + 1 stake per your (constructive!) post in translated thread . WhitePaper translation: 80 stakes pre-ICO-website translation: 50 stakes  Apply here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdye4RzY22Dr5YQYVDqZIyKInoebnoCSEWnQ32ZEBP5fkLgeQ/viewform?usp=sf_link  Statuses of reserved translations: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wdH69iQtTO6dnj1X_Rn0HJZ1i7cnCmZSS6ivQT5fvc0/edit?usp=sharing   3: Articles and Media - 20%  Write an article or create a video about DentalFix or/and Dental First Aid Kit technology and earn DentalFix tokens!  Accepted languages: English, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Indonesian, Russian, Korean,German, French.  Article/Blog Rules:  1. Your text must be original. 2. Your text must contain at least 500 words. 3. Your post must include links to our pre-ICO website or/and to our bitcointalk thread. (http://www.che-ss.com/dentalfix-ico/ https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=1999784.0 ) 4. You should be very familiar with Dental First Aid Kit idea (if no, please re-read our whitepaper and articles from the main thread). 5. Please include your bitcointalk name in the bottom of article. 6. Website there you will publish your article  should have at least 5K visitors per month. (we willll check it via Similarweb)  Stakes number will be depends on article quality:  - Bad - 0 stakes - Normal - 10 Stakes - Medium - 30 Stakes - Good -  50 Stakes  Media/Video Rules:  1. Your video must be original. 2. You video must be at least 2 minutes long. 3. Your video must explain Dental First Aid Kit idea or/and how it works. 4. Video resolution should be at least 720p. 5. Please include your bitcointalk name in the video description.  Stakes number will be depends on video quality AND number of views:  - Bad - 0 stakes - Normal - 10 Stakes - Medium - 30 Stakes - Good -  50 Stakes  - If number of views will be more 1000 you will receive +30% stakes - If number of views will be more 10 000 we will double your stakes  Submit Your Articles and Video here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScpq7raVQedF6dy_UoiwBGEOxTxIQHyiZbdP9SgIawrSZTZ9g/viewform?usp=sf_link  See Status: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1o6qppPWEs29ouCK5VDiAGApg2dHHs3xw3qbjMrwPHZI/edit?usp=sharing  4: Social Media Campaign (Facebook and Twitter) - 20%  We will frequently post some updates and announcements. You will be earn stake(s) for each:  - retweet/repost - tweet mentioning @DentalfixK twitter account and/or  including DentalFix pre-ICO website (http://www.che-ss.com/dentalfix-ico/ ) and #DentalFix hashtag - FB post mentioning @DentalFix facebook page (https://www.facebook.com/DentalfixK/ )and/or  including DentalFix pre-ICO website (http://www.che-ss.com/dentalfix-ico/) and # DentalFix hashtag.  Stakes number will be depends on you followers number:  - Under 500 followers: 1 stake - 501-1000 followers: 2 stakes - 1001 or more followers: 4 stakes  Rules:  - Only 1 account per person is allowed - Your account must have at least 200 real followers . - Only 1 post/repost/tweet/retweet per day will be counted. - Twitter account followers will be based on an audit from twitteraudit.com - You should retweet/repost only a post that is no older than one week.
